title: Import by guess
content:
Hmph. So I'm trying to import my links from del.icio.us to Yahoo!'s My Web to no avail. While I do have around 5750 links posted to del.icio.us, the export looks like it's clean XML. But, my only report from Y! is basically, "Well, that didn't work. Try it again."

    or just use http://feedmelinks.com/import/ -- we import del.icio.us-format XML.
